WEBVTT

00:00:29.160 --> 00:00:30.600
and we put our stuff in there.

00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:33.216
And then she said, "Go over to the circle

00:00:33.240 --> 00:00:35.520
and play with the kids
until class starts."

00:00:36.160 --> 00:00:39.616
So I went over there
and plopped down like I owned the place,

00:00:39.640 --> 00:00:41.056
and I'm playing,

00:00:41.080 --> 00:00:42.985
and all of a sudden, the boy next to me,

00:00:43.009 --> 00:00:46.056
he was wearing a white shirt
with blue shorts.

00:00:46.080 --> 00:00:47.800
I remember it like it was yesterday.

00:00:48.840 --> 00:00:51.496
Suddenly he stopped playing and he said,

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:53.120
"Why are you so short?"

00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:56.816
And I just kept playing.
I didn't think he was talking to me.

00:00:56.840 --> 00:00:57.856
(Laughter)

00:00:57.880 --> 00:00:59.696
And in a louder voice, he said,

00:00:59.720 --> 00:01:02.000
"Hey, why are you so short?"